receiver.name: self
receiver.value:
RankSerializer(read_only=True):
    id = IntegerField(label='ID', read_only=True)
    name = CharField(max_length=255)
    slug = CharField(max_length=255, validators=[<UniqueValidator(queryset=Rank.objects.all())>])
    description = SerializerMethodField()
    title = CharField(allow_blank=True, allow_null=True, max_length=255, required=False)
    css_class = CharField(allow_blank=True, allow_null=True, max_length=255, required=False)
    is_default = BooleanField(required=False)
